    List Authors

    hf_list_authors.Rd

    List Model Authors

    hf_list_authors(pattern = NULL)

    Arguments

    pattern

    A search term or regular expression. Defaults to NULL (return all results).

    See also

    https://huggingface.co/docs/hub/searching-the-hub

    Examples
